HEADWORD: Argil
<hw>Ar"gil</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>argile</ets>, L. <ets>argilla</ets> white clay, akin to Gr. <?/ or
<?/ argil, <?/ white. See <er>Argent</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
<def>Clay, or potter's earth; sometimes pure clay, or alumina. See
<er>Clay</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
